            <h4>Free tools are great — until posting becomes the bottleneck.</h4>
            <p>theStacc Social writes, designs, and auto-publishes posts to Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, X, and GBP. <strong>From $49/mo, no scheduling tool to babysit.</strong></p>
